This file describes the convention for naming run directories.
The reference case is:

run_taux2000_rb0110[_kv0000]

Four significant figures are given for each parameter

- taux = zonal wind stress magnitude,
         units: 10^-4 N m^-2
         (so taux2000 = 0.2 N m^-2)

- rb =   linear bottom drag parameter
         units: 10^-5 m s^-1
         (so rb0110 = 1.1E-3 m/s)
         corresponds with MITgcm parameter bottomDragLinear

- kv =   vertical diffusivity
         units: 10^-6 m s^-2
         [if specified, otherwise assumed zero]
